bilingual.source: The probe enters the Earth-Mars transfer orbit.
bilingual.target: 探测器进入地火转移轨道。
质粒可以在细菌之间转移。

bilingual.source: Please transfer the funds to my account.
bilingual.target: 请将资金转移到我的账户。

bilingual.source: We can transfer funds through the bank.
bilingual.target: 我们可以通过银行转移资金。

bilingual.source: Please transfer the files to this folder.
bilingual.target: 请将文件转移到这个文件夹里。

bilingual.source: He decided to transfer to another company.
bilingual.target: 他决定转移到另一家公司工作。

bilingual.source: You can use online banking to transfer funds.
bilingual.target: 你可以使用银行转账来转移资金。

bilingual.source: Can you transfer this file to my computer?
bilingual.target: 你能把这个文件转移到我的电脑上吗？

bilingual.source: The scientist used a dropper to transfer the chemical.
bilingual.target: 科学家用滴管转移化学物质。

bilingual.source: The social security system relies on transfer payment.
bilingual.target: 社会保障系统依赖于转移支付。

list.abstract: 《transfer》是周传雄的国语摇滚专辑，于2000年12月25日由索尼音乐发行，专辑收录了《忘记》《心结》《记事本》等十二首歌曲。

transfer vt.使转移; 使调动; 转让（权利等）; 让与 vi.转让; 转学; 转乘; 转会（尤指职业足球队） n.转移; 调动; 换乘; （运动员）转会
n.传送，传递

yingyinNormal.en: No, but can you. Can you transfer my files so I can use them at home?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，但你能不能转移我的文件，这样我可以在家里使用？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to attempt an experiment that will get you to transfer those feelings to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我准备尝试一个实验让你将这些情感转移到我身上。

yingyinNormal.en: Until such time as I am able to transfer my consciousness I shall remain in a secure location and interact with the world in this manner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，在我能够转移意识之前，我的肉身将保存在一个安全地点，并借此方式同外界联系。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you. Oh, you're gonna need transfer slips.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢您啦。你们需要个转班证明。

yingyinNormal.en: Ooh, be sure to keep an eye on which credits transfer to a four-year college.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对了，记得注意下哪些学分是能转修成四年制大学的。

yingyinNormal.en: So, you don't want to transfer? Not really, sir. I'm terribly sorry. Excuse me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你不想转部门吗？不想，真的非常抱歉。不好意思。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't belong here anymore as a client. We'll transfer your files to your home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不再是这里的客户了，我们会把你的文件送到你家。

yingyinNormal.en: If you requested to transfer, we can make that happen. If that's what you'd prefer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你想转部门，我们可以做到。如果你想要我转走的话。

yingyinNormal.en: And then really that's ready. So you can either drain it or transfer it straight to the plate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就可以出锅了，可以沥干一会儿，也可直接装盘。

yingyinNormal.en: The time has come to dissolve the IMF. Mr. Chairman. And transfer the salvageable assets to the CIA.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是时候解散碟中谍小组了。主席先生。然后把其资源和人员调拨给中情局。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm gonna transfer all the data and bring it to you. You need to see this. I'll be in my office. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我把所有数据都传输一下，拿来给你看，你必须看看。我在办公室等你。好的。

yingyinNormal.en: I want to transfer all the women from this boat into that boat right now. As quick as you can, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 女士们到另一艘船上，尽快，拜托了。

yingyinNormal.en: You know what we're gonna do, Matthews? We're gonna transfer out of here. Yeah. Yeah? Yeah. Lucas? Farkle?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道我们接下来打算怎么做吗，麦修斯？我们要转出这个班。卢卡斯，弗科？

yingyinNormal.en: They became targets, using insects to transfer the right pollen to the right plant, even over great distances.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样有的放矢，即使距离很远，昆虫也能够将花粉传递到与之匹配的花朵上。

yingyinNormal.en: Batroc was hired anonymously to attack the Lemurian Star and he was contacted by email and paid by wire transfer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 巴托克被匿名雇佣袭击利莫里亚之星，他们用电子邮件联系，费用是电子转账的。

yingyinNormal.en: Theresa may have been trying to use the woodcutter as a mule, and when that failed, then may have tried to do the transfer personally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 特蕾莎或许之前想利用伐木工代劳，但后来失败了，她便想亲自来完成传输。

yingyinNormal.en: The children in the Caterpillar Room are not age-appropriate for me and my friends. We respectfully request a transfer to the Butterfly Room.
yingyinNormal.zh: 毛毛虫小儿室的孩子们对我和我的朋友来说不合适，我们很恳请去蝴蝶屋。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd see this a lot in narcotics. People who know their money's being watched just transfer their funds to somewhere much less monitored. Less monitored. Like where?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在调查毒品案件的时候看过很多类似的事情。人们知道自己的钱一直被监管着就把他们的资金转到缺少监管的地方。缺少监管的地方。哪里？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Ferraro suggests the results may <highlight>transfer</highlight> to other parts of Asia.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 费拉罗认为，这一结果可能会转移到亚洲其他地区。

examination_example.sentence: Called conditional cash <highlight>transfers</highlight> or CCTs, these social assistance programs are designed to reduce inequality and break the cycle of poverty.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 称为有条件现金转移或CCT，这些社会援助计划旨在减少不平等和打破贫困循环。

examination_example.sentence: Five minutes after that, we placed either bacon or bread on the surface for 5, 30 or 60 seconds, and then measured the number of bacteria <highlight>transferred</highlight> to the food.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 五分钟后，我们将培根或面包放在表面上5秒、30秒或60秒，然后测量转移到食物上的细菌数量。

examination_example.sentence: We wanted to know if the length of time food is in contact with a contaminated surface affected the rate of <highlight>transfer</highlight> of bacteria to the food.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们想知道食物与受污染表面接触的时间长短是否会影响细菌向食物转移的速度。

examination_example.sentence: When a carpet was contaminated, less than 1% of the bacteria were <highlight>transferred</highlight>. But when the food was in contact with tile or wood, 45-70% of bacteria were.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当地毯被污染时，只有不到1%的细菌被转移。但当食物与瓷砖或木头接触时，45-70%的细菌被转移了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: move from one place to another

examination_example.sentence: However, the director of the hospital said the patient couldn't be <highlight>transferred</highlight> unless he paid his bill first.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，医院的院长说，除非病人先付账，否则就不能转院。

examination_example.sentence: Thanks to her help, the patient was at once <highlight>transferred</highlight> to another hospital and his life was saved.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由于她的帮助，病人一下子被转到了另一家医院，他的生命得到了挽救。

examination_example.sentence: After <highlight>transferring</highlight> his blood, the boy asked his mother, " Mom, how long can I live from now on? "
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在转移血液后，男孩问他的母亲：" 妈妈，我以后能活多久？"

sense_info_list.en: to change to a different vehicle during a journey; to arrange for sb to change to a different vehicle during a journey

examination_example.sentence: I am home to China’s largest railway <highlight>transfer</highlight> center.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我的家是中国最大的铁路换乘中心。

sense_info_list.en: to copy information, music, an idea, etc. from one method of recording or presenting it to another; to be recorded or presented in a different way

examination_example.sentence: At first I write the stories by hand, and then I <highlight>transfer</highlight>（转录）them onto a computer.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我首先手写故事，然后转录到电脑上。
